<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NMT56">
<l>avarivareṉ ṟillai yaṉaṅkavēḷ tātaik</l>
<l>kevaru metirillai kaṇṭī ruvarik</l>
<l>kaṭalṉañca muṇṭāṉ kaṭaṉeṉṟu vāṇaṟ</l>
<l>kuṭaṉiṉṟu tōṟṟā ṉoruṅku.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Not [just] that man or this man: look, no one equals the Father of the bodiless Kāma!</l>
<l>[Śiva] who drank poison from the ocean of brackish water</l>
<l>Stood by Bāṇa saying [that it was his] duty</l>
<l>and lost together [with him].</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
